Procedure MaximumOfThreeNumbers
  READ input from user and store it in variable A
  READ input from user and store it in variable B
  READ input from user and store it in variable C
  IF A is greater than B THEN
    IF A is greater than C THEN
      SHOW A is the maximum of three numbers
    ELSE 
      SHOW C is the maximum of three numbers
    ENDIF
  ELSE
    IF B is greater than C THEN
      SHOW B is the maximum of three numbers
    ELSE 
      SHOW C is the maximum of three numbers
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
End Procedure
